    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sprinkle your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> over the meat-free chick'n and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until warmed through – this is your <strong>Mediterranean-style meat-free chick'n</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1678902525282-x200.jpg",
