      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Dress the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
