    {
      "instruction": "<p>Load up the <strong>warmed naan</strong> with the <strong>Greek-style salad</strong> and <strong>Mediterranean-style meat-free chick'n</strong></p><p>Dollop over the <strong>tzatziki mayo</strong> and garnish with the<strong> remaining chopped parsley</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> dressed shredded lettuce</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
